Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Occupy now or renew existing lease

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer 14 Clearview Place, Brookvale to the market for sale. Located in a tightly held suburb, the property is a true standalone offering that will appeal to occupiers and investors alike.

The property itself has an impressive site area of 1,790* sqm and a building area of 1,501* sqm. The warehouse is access via a wide driveway and large container height roller shutter door.

The property is occupied on a monthly licence agreement creating an opportunity for the astute investor to renew and extend the lease or for an occupier to move in upon settlement.

We strongly encourage your consideration of this free standing opportunity in one of the northern beaches most popular industrial areas. The property will be sold via Auction on Tuesday, 30 September 2014.

Property Highlights include:

- Warehouse area: 1,066* sqm
- Office area: 435* sqm
- Land area: 1,790* sqm
- 20 car parks
- Freehold title
- IN1 General Industrial
- Occupy immediately or renew the existing lease

*approximate

CBRE are pleased to offer this rare industrial opportunity for lease in the heart of Brookvale’s tightly held industrial precinct.

The property offers an efficient high clearance regular shaped warehouse which is accessed via two container height roller shutters with internal clearance to 7.5m*. 

The property is located within walking distance to public transport, cafes, gyms and major arterial roads.

Property particulars:

+ 106sqm* of office 
+ 732sqm* of warehouse
+ 63sqm* of bonus mezzanine/warehouse office
+ separate warehouse and office amenities with shower facilities 
+ Newly renovated open plan office
+ High Clearance warehouse to 7.5m
+ Two (2) container height roller shutter
+ Undercover awning 
+ Excellent truck access
+ Hardstand for container drop-off
+ Secure site
+ Ample parking 
+ Over Head gantry crane
+ High power supply
+ Central location to amenities and public transport 
+ Available NOW!

CBRE is delighted to present for sale or lease a rare main road frontage site in the tightly held market of Brookvale. 762-770 Pittwater Rd is offered to market via expressions of interest closing 6th March 2015 at 4.00pm.

The subject property comprises an expansive 4,870m2 (approx) site area capturing a frontage to Pittwater Rd of 60m together with a 65m frontage and dual access via West St. We firmly believe this is a genuinely rare opportunity and one without comparison in the current market.

Current improvements comprise of a fully functional car dealership centre including a showroom, offices, a service centre, and an expansive hardstand. Fronting West Street are two industrial properties with a site area totalling 1,119sqm. The properties are currently fully leased on flexible terms allowing for investment or vacant possession.

The offering is further enhanced by way of an existing, approved DA for a further 3 levels commercial, retail or automotive development fronting Pittwater Rd which could add further improvements of 3,210sqm.

This property presents a real business opportunity for a investor or developer to lease, invest or redevelop in a rare prime main road opportunity.

This outstanding opportunity is formally offered via an Expressions of Interest campaign closing 6th March 2015 at 4.00pm.
